metadata.name: Power of Women
metadata.description:
This is being made by me because I want to help my girlfriend with cost of education. As we all know this can be very expensive and can put people in crippling debt. We have a young girl together and we both want to make sure she has an amazing life. She works full time, a mother and going to college full time. As long as I known her she has worked so hard to get to where she is. For anyone that mints we really appreciate your support.

Please understand there will be nothing behind this, no burn, no utility and this will stay open till we get the funds we need for her education.
